Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail 146 Trans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.72,0:00:05.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After the new Oracion Seis appeared \Nbefore Natsu and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:09.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,they were at their wit's end, as the \NInfinity Clock was stolen from them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:12.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and their mission to recover \Nit ended in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the Celestial Spirit Wizards' \Nbiological links were broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:19.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Infinity Clock's \Ntrue nature was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:24.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, time itself began to fall into chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:02:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You say the person who broke out the \Nimprisoned new Oracion Seis was Cardinal Rapowant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:03.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. I believe it's indisputable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.27,0:02:06.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The time isn't right yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand how big Zentopia is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:18.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doranbolt, I'm sorry to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:27.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.05,0:02:30.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm disgusted with myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in leading the \NEnforcement and Detention Corps
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,if I can't take action during a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:39.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:43.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we do everything that we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:45.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Doranbolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.32,0:02:49.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us, Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Time's Chaos upon us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:56.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why has the Infinity Clock appeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean the destruction \Nof civilization?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us, Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.63,0:03:08.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:13.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zentopia's way of \Nputting the world in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And after this purge is complete, \Nthe world will be reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and we will begin to walk upon a new path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting the world in order...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the new Oracion \NSeis to destroy churches,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,disrupting Celestial Spirit \NWizards' biological links,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and throwing time into chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.30,0:03:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really putting the world in order?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:46.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Without offering any answers, that \Ngirl Lucy is being sacrificed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:50.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and my duty to protect \Nthe Infinity Clock is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiral of Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:02.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Ichiya, and this handpicked \Nteam of Fairy Tail members
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:11.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,will most definitely save \NLucy-san and Natsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:16.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of my sister, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who pitted herself against \NRacer so we could charge ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way, Lucy and Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope those two are okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu promised it'd be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Natsu's okay, I'm \Npositive Lucy's okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:39.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I have the same feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira is gonna be okay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Man to have faith like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.11,0:04:46.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole bunch wears rose-colored glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Redesigned Christina, \Nmagic bomber of my guild,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:52.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Pegasus, the pride of the continent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're nearing Zentopia Cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you intend to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the archbishop is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:04.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.66,0:05:08.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the archbishop's the guy who used \NMichelle and did all this mean-spirited crap,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:14.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lackeys, get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:19.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are still around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True evil never goes on the lam empty-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:26.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Infinity Clock isn't doable, \Nwe'll make do with another treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.67,0:05:33.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, knock yourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will, we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:38.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lackeys, begin the treasure hunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:49.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't even be worth using \NRupture Magic on you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:57.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cleaner... Gatman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:05.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've got quite \Na lot of magic in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful. He's an extremely \Ndangerous opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Now I'm gettin' fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, deployments are complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.07,0:06:18.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about confirming my order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:38.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The army is in disorder, too, men...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is also an effect of Real Nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ain't... nothin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this any time for clowning around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:50.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:52.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:55.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:58.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! You've become an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've turned into a raccoon, Carla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.53,0:07:03.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're now a dog, Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good. Everyone's fallen under \Nthe influence of Real Nightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:12.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Then why am I fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use this ancient weapon \Nthat's said to keep evil at bay
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to cut through the Real Nightmare vibrations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning you hit us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:51.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the archbishop's bedroom \Nwould be under heavy guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we got in here relatively easily, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:55.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.02,0:08:03.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shhh! The archbishop is in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a pain in the ass. \NLet's quit with the hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:08.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the archbishop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:19.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zentopia's way of \Nputting the world in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's somethin' I wanna ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:25.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give me an honest answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:29.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:32.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zentopia's way of \Nputting the world in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listenin' to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There is nothing to worry about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:39.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:43.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is Zentopia's way of \Nputting the world in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:47.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone is using magic \Nto control the archbishop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:56.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentopia's Cardinal Rapowant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:03.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you're Gildarts \Nfrom Fairy Tail, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I guess my reputation precedes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:11.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never figured even a cardinal \Nof Zentopia would know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's an autograph \Nyou want, I gotta decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:15.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy at the moment, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.19,0:09:18.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I give you two credit for making it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:22.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't get out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun. Let's see what ya got.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:47.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can... catch up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.57,0:10:02.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Faster...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be... faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your speed increased even more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:44.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How... can you be faster... than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:49.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:54.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:12:00.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In a confrontation, the person \Nwho wants to help their friends
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is stronger than the person who escapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you running away from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:16.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I... running away from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always... running away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were running away from \Nyourself, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:32.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,From... myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:35.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. From your own past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pain, failure, fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:44.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A painful past that made \Nyou want to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:47.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the same way once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept running from my bitter past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I understand... \Nthe pain in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:24.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to chase you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone is calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to look for that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.08,0:14:07.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Racer failed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:12.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra, Angel, stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zentopia's doctrine demands absolute loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:24.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never doubt never doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if you doubt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.76,0:14:31.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Traitors... will scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic that makes you \Nexplode... Rupture Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:41.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I expand the magic that's in your body in \Nthe blink of an eye and make it explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:49.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care who it is that defies \NZentopia's doctrine, I'll clean them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a fool outta me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.49,0:14:58.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:06.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll dance with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice rupture!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.54,0:15:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll keep dancing until there's \Nno more magic left in your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:26.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't got time to scrap \Nwith a clown like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can have the last \Ndance first, Natsu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:34.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it so you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:42.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:46.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that anyone who opposed \NHis Grace had to be a bad guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:50.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but between you and the new Oracion Seis,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:53.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost the ability to \Ntell who the bad guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:56.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:06.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to be able to \Nmove to use Rupture Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:21.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like... making someone freeze...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:22.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is all I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:34.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, I want you to at least confirm \Nwith your own eyes what's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.64,0:16:53.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:55.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them near the cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the redesigned Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:04.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:10.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.02,0:17:15.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:22.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They've shaken my faith in Zentopia, \Nbut I won't let them do as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.72,0:17:24.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Kanaloa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,An octopus is no match for \Nmy redesigned Christina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They all bounced off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...dangerous parfum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:55.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the rest to you, Kanaloa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:02.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to His Grace \Nand ask him directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:07.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, what happened seven \Nyears ago will occur again...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire spiral anchors!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The redesigned Christina and I will \Ntake care of this octopus by ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we do, though, everyone get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ichiya-san, you'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind me! Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go... my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:50.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichiya-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard, actin' so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:07.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Man among men!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:11.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how dangerous the circumstances, \NIchiya always manages to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:14.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to rescue Natsu and Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.83,0:19:21.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:27.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zentopia's way of \Nputting the world in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:30.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:36.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you escaped your cell too, did you, Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Holiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.79,0:19:45.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Dragneel... a Dragon Wizard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You smell the same as Master Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Zero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if he's Master Zero or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but this bastard is definitely the one \Nwho's mind controlling the archbishop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts' voice reached me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.58,0:20:14.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, Cardinal Rapowant is \Nmind controlling the archbishop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:15.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rapowant is controlling His Grace...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:23.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:28.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...borrowed His Grace's authority \Nto use me like a puppet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You! You'll pay for this, Rapowant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:36.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're the asshole \Ncontrolling the archbishop,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:40.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you must be the same asshole who \Nused Michelle to trick us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:41.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:45.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious! I'm gonna \Nmop the floor with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now... I'm the one who's \Ngonna mop the floor with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts... Let me do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two hotheads...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:00.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:05.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you love to fight that much, you \Ntwo might as well fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:07.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't do as I say, \Nher life is forfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.30,0:21:14.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch, this ain't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you fool me, Rapowant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.35,0:21:23.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dear comrades are coming, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:52.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My comrades are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Fairy Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But they'll lose their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Why will \Nthey lose their lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:04.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:09.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They adore you so much, they'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:10.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone have you, Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:17.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:22.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Become an adult, become a kid, \Nwhat the hell's goin' on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:23:59.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's become warped!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:02.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop it fast, \Nthere'll be big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:05.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Big trouble"... Specifically, \Nwhat's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna delve into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:09.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't know the reason, \NI can't get fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:11.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Lucy's still captured \Nand there are plenty other points
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.37,0:24:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,for you to get fired up about.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.98,0:24:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: To the Infinity Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:20.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but still, it keeps sticking in \Nmy mind, it's like a pent-up feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.56,0:24:23.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that! Hurry up and go save Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.77,0:24:25.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
